Usage: moo list [STRING] [options]

  Options:
    -d, --[no-]details               Display detailed information of gem(s)
    -l, --local                      Restrict operations to the LOCAL domain
    -r, --remote                     Restrict operations to the REMOTE domain
        --source NAME|URL            Use URL as the remote source for gems

  Common Options:
    -h, --help                       Get help on this command
    -V, --verbose                    Set the verbose level of output

  Arguments:
    STRING        start of package name to look for

  Summary:
    Display packages whose name starts with STRING

  Defaults:
    --local --no-details

